body_html: Try in a virtual environment. Afaik, that output isn't an error. It's saying that an upgraded version of tf has already been installed. Also pip is pointing to your system python. Not anaconda python. Execute which pip to confirm this. Also, very less people use python2 now.

body: Try in a virtual environment. Afaik, that output isn't an error. It's saying that an upgraded version of tf has already been installed. Also pip is pointing to your system python. Not anaconda python. Execute `which pip` to confirm this. Also, very less people use python2 now.
